The paper analyzes the impact of depositing articles in the arXiv on their citation rates and publisher downloads. The study focuses on mathematics journals, but the findings may be relevant to other fields as well. The paper does not deal with any specific computer science subfield, but the analysis methods and results are likely to be of interest to researchers in several areas, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), cryptography (cs.CR), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
